name: 4" Premium Alternating Air Pressure Relief Mattress
description:
4" Premium Alternating Air Pressure Relief Mattres

This 4” premium mattress consists of 24 rectangular air cells (with 8 ventilation cells) with low air loss function to further optimise pressure and weight redistribution. This helps to minimise user's discomfort during alternating.

Pillow function maintains the 4 air cells at the head of bed in static mode for added comfort. Each air cell is easily removable and replaceable.

Nylon zipped mattress cover is water resistant, vapour permeable, machine washable and low shear safeguarding user's skin and comfort.
